    "content": "UG seriously needs more Wham! basslines! There fantastic lines!\r\n\r\nBassist - Deon Estus (look into him hes great.)\r\nSong - Freedom\r\n\r\nIf im wrong on any part correct me! Instead of telling me im wrong show me please!\r\n\r\nSpecial thanks to jack.sonic for helping me with where to start! thanks man!\r\n\r\nWham! - Freedom\r\n\r\n[tab]Intro\r\nG-------------|\r\nD---2-3-------| 4x\r\nA-3----------2|\r\nE-------1-3-5-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 2x\r\nG--------------|\r\nD-3-3---1---1--|\r\nA-----3---3---3| 2x\r\nE--------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G--------------|\r\nD--------------|\r\nA-3-3---2---2--| 2x\r\nE-----3---3---3|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G--------------|\r\nD-3-3---1---1--|\r\nA-----3---3---3| 2x\r\nE--------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G------------|\r\nD---------23-|\r\nA-3-22-00----|\r\nE------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nPre Chorus\r\n\r\n[tab]G---------------------------|\r\nD---------------------23----|\r\nA-------------33-22-00------| 2x\r\nE-11-11-33-33---------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]And you doo\r\nG------------|\r\nD------------|\r\nA------------|\r\nE-11-11-33-33|[/tab]\r\n\r\nI dont need your freedom ect.\r\n\r\n[tab]G-------------------|\r\nD------2-3---3-2----|\r\nA-3-33--------------|\r\nE----------1--------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G-------------------|\r\nD------2-3---3-2----|\r\nA-5~~---------------|\r\nE----------1--------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G-------------------|\r\nD------2-3---3-2----|\r\nA-3-33--------------|\r\nE----------1--------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G-------------------|\r\nD------2-3---3-2----|\r\nA-5~~---------------|\r\nE----------1--------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G-------------------|\r\nD------2-3---3~-----|\r\nA-3-33--------------|\r\nE----------1--------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G----------|\r\nD-------5--|\r\nA-5-7-8----|\r\nE----------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nStop!\r\nGirl all I want is you!\r\n\r\n[tab]G-------------|\r\nD---2-3-------| 4x\r\nA-3----------2|\r\nE-------1-3-5-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 2x\r\nG--------------|\r\nD-3-3---1---1--